{"tid":2362783,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你媽 N賓判刑冇人講？","createTime":"2021-01-11T16:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T03:19:40.000Z","uid":35348,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c47f0e38473ff46c32de74178e69f2de10d72347","tid":2362783,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"油站職員聲稱因不忿其信奉印度教的友人經常來電滋擾，遂於去年向跑馬地一間印度廟的神像投擲生肉。職員早前承認作出有違公德的行為罪，今在東區裁判法院被判接受15個月感化令。暫委裁判官陳志輝判刑指，即使不滿意對方的行為，亦不可影響他人的宗教。<br />\n<br />\n跑馬地黃泥涌道1號印度廟宇，作出性質令人憎惡的有違公德的行為，即向一印度教神像投擲生肉。<br />\n陳官今指，早前法庭為被告索取的感化官報告內容正面，從中感到被告的深切悔意，因此法庭願意接受感化官的判刑建議，惟被告須遵守三項條件，包括接受心理及精神治療課程。<br />\n【案件編號：ESCC2324/20】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jnq4maVOmrVWT9h0moZzGbZ9TAU=/538x302/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FDXKY7W6OXY6J3NR2JZWSOXT4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fjnq4maVOmrVWT9h0moZzGbZ9TAU%3D%2F538x302%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFDXKY7W6OXY6J3NR2JZWSOXT4U.jpg&h=e3e504f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告莫湛深(蒙頭者)"},{"pid":"873d5f9a87c6911bd6f9df2d2e6338874c5a0804","tid":2362783,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"莫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccf0ef6fbbb7a7ccebe4d1daba79e1d1d9e81d2","tid":2362783,"uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"嗰隻鬼黎 由佢死啦"},{"pid":"b16fdcbbda00744695e5fc7ca91458d498eb8d1f","tid":2362783,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"873d5f9a87c6911bd6f9df2d2e6338874c5a0804","tid":2362783,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"莫生<img src=\"